34 executive training program. The executive training program must
35 include training in the following areas:
36 (1) Liability.
37 (2) Media relations.
38 (3) Accounting and administration.
39 (4) Discipline.
40 (5) Department policy making.
41 (6) Lawful use of force and de-escalation training.
42 (7) Department programs.
