38 (1) must be:
39 (A) measured from the outer edges of the regularly used
40 building, parking lot, storage areas, or processing areas of
41 the commercial or industrial activity; and
42 (B) parallel to the edge of the pavement of the highway;
ES 80—LS 6159/DI 112

39
1 and
2 (2) may not be measured from the property line of the
3 commercial or industrial activity, unless the property line is
4 located on an area described in subdivision (1)(A).
