11 (C) qualifications for career coaches and a training program to
12 enable the career coaches to provide relevant information to
13 the individuals being served;
14 (D) the incorporation and ongoing usage of Internet based
15 systems that are interoperable with the comprehensive career
16 navigation and coaching system; and
17 (E) career exploration, engagement, and experience.
