36 (B) other sexual conduct (as defined in IC 35-31.5-2-221.5);
37 or
38 (C) any fondling or touching with the child with the intent to
39 arouse or satisfy the sexual desires of the child or the
40 workplace supervisor;
41 commits child seduction.
